OL,3,C7-year-old boy 'seriously' injured
OL,4,Cafter attack by family's XL Bully
OL,6,FA 7-year-old boy needed surgery after
OL,7,Fhe was bitten by the family's XL Bully.
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire Police said it
OL,10,Fhappened at around 8pm on Monday in
OL,11,Fthe kitchen of the family home in
OL,12,FHatfield, Doncaster.
OL,14,FThe schoolboy was left with serious
OL,15,Finjuries to his neck, which required
OL,16,Fsurgery.
OL,18,FLater that same evening, officers
OL,19,Freceived a call at 11.36pm that
OL,20,Fanother child had been mauled by a
OL,21,FShih Tzu, at a house in Doncaster.
