OL,9,FBoth dogs were been seized by officers.
OL,11,FThe force said they received 15 calls
OL,12,Fof dogs "dangerously" out of control
OL,13,Fwithin the 24 hours, requesting
OL,14,Fofficer assistance at emergency dog
OL,15,Fbites, or making police aware of out
OL,16,Fof control dogs.
