OL,3,C7-year-old boy 'seriously' injured
OL,4,Cafter attack by family's XL Bully
OL,6,FThey said: "Any dog of any breed can
OL,7,Fbite and cause harm or fear. It is
OL,8,Fimportant that you understand your
OL,9,Fdog, it's behaviour and ensure it has
OL,10,Fa safe space where it can be alone."
OL,12,FA spokesperson added: "You are more
OL,13,Flikely to be bitten and injured by a
OL,14,Fdog within your home, known to you,
OL,15,Fthan anywhere else."
OL,17,F"Simple changes can be the difference
OL,18,Fbetween life and death."
