OL,3,C7-year-old boy 'seriously' injured
OL,4,Cafter attack by family's XL Bully
OL,6,FOfficers have also urged the public to
OL,7,Ftake extra caution as children are
OL,8,Fspending more time at home and
OL,9,Fvisiting friends, family and local
OL,10,Fparks during the summer holidays.
OL,12,FIt became a criminal offence to own an
OL,13,Funregistered XL bully on 1 February
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FSince then South Yorkshire Police has
OL,17,Fseen a seven-fold increase in the
OL,18,Fnumber of dangerous dog seizures.
