OL,6,FThe force logged 1,800 incidents of
OL,7,Fowners allowing their dogs to be
OL,8,Fdangerously out of control last year,
OL,9,Fa 38% rise on the year before.
OL,11,FMore than 1,000 people were injured.
OL,12,FAlmost 350 incidents involved children
OL,13,Funder the age of 15, with 73 aged
OL,14,Fthree or under.
